ckpapershotgun.com/2010/09/28/a-deeper-dungeon-dungeon-keeperfx/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://keeper.lubiki.pl/html/dk_keeperfx_read.php|title=KeeperFX Readme file|accessdate=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160525202924/http://keeper.lubiki.pl/html/dk_keeperfx_read.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>游戏的续作《{{tsl|en|Dungeon Keeper 2}}》于1999年发行，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/games/dungeon-keeper-ii/pc-9944|title=Dungeon Keeper II – PC|accessdate=2016-11-20}}</ref>该系列由[[Mythic_Entertainment|Mythic Entertainment]]重新启动，并于2014年1月30日发布了面向[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]的重制（也称为{{tsl|en|Dungeon Keeper (2014 video game)||Dungeon Keeper}}）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.retrogamer.net/blog_post/dungeon-keeper-out-now-on-android-and-ios/|title=Dungeon Keeper Out Now On Android And iOS|accessdate=2016-11-20|date=2014-01-30|archive-date=2016-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120085052/http://www.retrogamer.net/blog_post/dungeon-keeper-out-now-on-android-and-ios/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Dungeon Keeper在日本的发行名称是Dungeon Keeper Premium{{Efn|{{nihongo|Dungeon Keeper Premium|ダンジョンキーパープレミアム}}}}，归属于EA Best Selection品牌<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.japan.ea.com/archive/dngn/findex.html|title=Dungeon Keeper|accessdate=2016-05-13|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990220144151/http://www.japan.ea.com/archive/dngn/findex.html|archivedate=1999-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2011年6月在[[GOG.com|gog.com]]上数字发行。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/06/03/good-old-games-add-good-old-ea-games/|title=Good Old Games Add Good Old EA Games|accessdate=2015-12-19|date=2011-06-03|last=Walker|first=John|publisher=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222131737/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/06/03/good-old-games-add-good-old-ea-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该游戏在2014年2月曾限免兑换几天。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/02/15/apologies-with-a-capital-ea-dungeon-keeper-free-on-gog/|title=Apologies With A Capital EA: Dungeon Keeper Free On GOG|accessdate=2016-05-14|date=2014-02-15|last=Grayson|first=Nathan|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813221249/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/02/15/apologies-with-a-capital-ea-dungeon-keeper-free-on-gog/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年10月，Dungeon Keeper允许在[[Origin_(电子游戏平台)|Origin]]上通过其“On The House”计划免费兑换。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/10/07/dungeon-keeper-free/#more-403973|title=Keep Forever: Dungeon Keeper Is Free Right Now|accessdate=2016-10-31|date=2016-10-07|last=Adam Smith|archive-date=2016-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019200952/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/10/07/dungeon-keeper-free/#more-403973|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://completegamereviews.com/original-dungeon-keeper-now-free-origin/|title=Original Dungeon Keeper now free on Origin|accessdate=2016-10-31|date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.